<br>
       I dont have a problem with that, but personally im damn tired of soloing! i have solo'd from lvl 39 to 51 now, and im tired of it. I want to be able to get a group in karnors or something every now and then instead of having to wait 2 hours for a group. Is it really all that much to ask for?<br>
<br>
       Maybe some idea's that would go along with our new found title of being a taxi, because it is painfully clear that they will not increase our dmg in our spells or reduce the amount of mana it takes to cast them. Anyone have any idea's that verant can shoot down without even reading? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cumdar>Cumdar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/01 1:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Can we get an enhancment that helps us get groups?</span><hr size=1> I think I can speak for VI when I say - NO.<br>
<br>
At least that is how it appears.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=anyentl>AnyenTL</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/01 1:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> nod</span><hr size=1> sadly, i must agree that how it appears, but there has got to be some way where we can get groups easyer.<br>
Something like sending a mob back to its bind point and clearing its aggro...... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujadrax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jadrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 232<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/01 6:54 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Can we get an enhancment that helps us get groups?</span><hr size=1> &lt;b&gt;Something like sending a mob back to its bind point and clearing its aggro......&lt;/b&gt;<br>
Prblem with this Idea is this, Its the disintegrate spell, with the advatage that you dont have to wait for respawn and the mob keeps its damage you have already done.<br>
You could 6 man almost all the mobs in the game with this baby, which makes it a little bit overpowered.<br>
